OL,3,CChiquita Banana must pay $38m to
OL,4,Cvictims of Columbian paramilitary it
OL,5,Cfunded
OL,7,FUS banana giant Chiquita has been
OL,8,Fordered to pay $38.3 million (#30
OL,9,Fmillion) to 16 family members of
OL,10,Fpeople killed by a right-wing
OL,11,Fparamilitary group it funded during
OL,12,Fthe Colombian civil war.
OL,14,FThe verdict from a Florida court marks
OL,15,Fthe first time that the company has
OL,16,Fbeen found liable in any of multiple
OL,17,Fsimilar cases pending across the US.
OL,19,FIt also marks a rare judgement blaming
OL,20,Fa private US company for human rights
OL,21,Fabuses in another country.
