OL,7,FThe group funded by Chiquita, United
OL,8,FSelf-Defence Forces of Colombia (AUC),
OL,9,Fhad been designated as a terror group
OL,10,Fby the US government in 2001.
OL,12,FThe AUC engaged in human rights abuses
OL,13,Facross Colombia, including murdering
OL,14,Fpeople it suspected to have links with
OL,15,Fleft-wing rebels.
OL,17,FAt its height the group had around
OL,18,F20,000 members and was financed
OL,19,Fthrough the drug trade, landowners,
OL,20,Fmining and petroleum firms and other
OL,21,Finternational companies.
