OL,7,FA ruling by the jury, which found that
OL,8,FChiquita was responsible for the
OL,9,Fwrongful deaths of eight men killed by
OL,10,Fthe AUC, comes after a 17-year legal
OL,11,Fbattle and represents the first time
OL,12,Fthat the fruit multinational company
OL,13,Fhas paid compensation to Colombian
OL,14,Fvictims, potentially paving the way
OL,15,Ffor others to lodge similar legal
OL,16,Faction.
