OL,7,F"The situation in Colombia was tragic
OL,8,Ffor so many," Chiquita, whose banana
OL,9,Foperations are based in Florida, said
OL,10,Fin a statement after the verdict.
OL,11,F"However, that does not change our
OL,12,Fbelief that there is no legal basis
OL,13,Ffor these claims."
OL,15,FWhat is Chiquita's connection with AUC?
OL,17,FAccording to court documents, Chiquita
OL,18,Fpaid the AUC about $1.7 million (#1.3
OL,19,Fmillion) between 1997 and 2004.
