OL,7,FThe AUC is blamed for the killings of
OL,8,Fthousands of people during those years.
OL,10,FChiquita has insisted that its
OL,11,FColombia subsidiary, Banadex, only
OL,12,Fmade the payments out of fear that AUC
OL,13,Fwould harm its employees and
OL,14,Foperations, court records show.
OL,16,FIn 2007, Chiquita pleaded guilty to a
OL,17,FUS criminal charge of engaging in
OL,18,Ftransactions with the foreign
OL,19,Fterrorist organisation and agreed to
OL,20,Fpay a $25 million (#19.5 million) fine.
