OL,7,FThe company was also required to
OL,8,Fimplement a compliance and ethics
OL,9,Fprogram, according to the Justice
OL,10,FDepartment.
OL,12,F"This verdict sends a powerful message
OL,13,Fto corporations everywhere: profiting
OL,14,Ffrom human rights abuses will not go
OL,15,Funpunished. These families, victimised
OL,16,Fby armed groups and corporations,
OL,17,Fasserted their power and prevailed in
OL,18,Fthe judicial process," Marco Simons,
OL,19,FEarthRights International General
OL,20,FCounsel said in a news release.
