OL,7,FColombian President Gustavo Petro
OL,8,Fquestioned why the US justice system
OL,9,Fcould "determine" Chiquita financed
OL,10,Fparamilitary groups, while judges in
OL,11,FColombia have not ruled against the
OL,12,Fcompany.
OL,14,F"The 2016 peace deal ... calls for the
OL,15,Fcreation of a tribunal that will
OL,16,Fdisclose judicial truths, why don't we
OL,17,Fhave one?" Petro posted on X,
OL,18,Freferencing the year the civil
OL,19,Fconflict ended.
