OL,7,FThe verdict followed a six-week trial
OL,8,Fand two days of deliberations. The
OL,9,FEarthRights case was originally filed
OL,10,Fin July 2007 and was combined with
OL,11,Fseveral other lawsuits.
OL,13,F"Our clients risked their lives to
OL,14,Fcome forward to hold Chiquita to
OL,15,Faccount, putting their faith in the
OL,16,FUnited States justice system. I am
OL,17,Fvery grateful to the jury for the time
OL,18,Fand care they took to evaluate the
OL,19,Fevidence," said Agnieszka Fryszman,
OL,20,Fanother lawyer in the case.
